quran[9{c,v,t}:
11,20,woh zameen mein Allah ko be bas karne walay nah thay aur nah Allah ke muqaabla mein koi un ka haami tha inhen ab dohra azaab diya jaye ga woh nah kisi ki sun hi satke thay aur nah khud hi inhen kuch sujhta tha
11,21,yeh woh log hain jinhon ne apne aap ko khud ghatay mein dala aur woh sab kuch un se khoya gaya jo unhon ne ghurr rakha tha
11,22,na Guzir hai ke wohi akhirat mein sab se barh kar ghatay mein rahen
11,23,"rahay woh log jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye aur apne rab hi ke ho kar rahay, to yaqeenan woh janati log hain aur jannat mein woh hamesha rahen ge"
11,24,"inn dono fareeqon ki misaal aisi hai jaisay aik aadmi to ho andha berha aur dosra ho dekhnay aur suneney wala, kya yeh dono yaksaa ho satke hain? kya tum ( iss misaal se ) koi sabaq nahi letay ?"
11,25,"( aur aisay hi halaat thay jab ) hum ne Nooh ko uss ki qoum ki taraf bheja tha ( uss ne kaha )"" mein tum logon ko saaf saaf khabardaar karta hon"
11,26,"ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karo warna mujhe andesha hai ke tum par aik roz dard naak azaab aeye ga """
11,27,"jawab mein uss ki qoum ke sardar, jinhon ne is ki baat maan-ne se inkaar kya tha, bolay"" hamari nazar mein to tum is ke siwa kuch nahi ho ke bas aik ensaan ho hum jaisay aur hum dekh rahay hain ke hamari qoum mein se bas unn logon ne jo hamaray haan اrazil )kamtar) thay be soochey samjhay tumhari pairwi ikhtiyar kar li hai aur hum koi cheez bhi aisi nahi paate jis mein tum log hum se kuch barhay hue ho, balkay hum to tumhe jhoota samajte hain """
11,28,"is ne kaha"" ae baradran qoum, zara socho to sahi ke agar mein apne rab ki taraf se aik khuli shahadat par qaim tha aur phir is ne mujh ko apni khaas rehmat se bhi Nawaz diya magar woh tum ko nazar nah aayi to aakhir hamaray paas kya zareya hai ke tum maanna nah chaho aur hum zabardasti is ko tumahray sir chipka den ?"
